data.description: Spectacular waterfront views throughout this one owner custom home. The open floor plan & gourmet kitchen include gas cooking, SS & granite countertops & dining area that opens to the back yard patio. The lovely fenced backyard is ready to be enjoyed. Five off street parking spaces/two car garage. Theatre furniture can convey. Great location, close to shopping, golf courses, military bases, beaches, & amazing restaurants. Enjoy nature paths around the lake & paddle boarding, swimming, canoe & kayaking. This four bedroom three & a half bath home is ready for you to call home!
